{"tid":1765228,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"(音樂)【12.7揭盅】《願榮光》狂吸12萬Like未入圍 網民推爆攞叱咤我最喜愛歌曲","createTime":"2019-12-01T16:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T04:00:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f123dc80b3983a267fdc2fcbea032cd1b750d2d0","tid":1765228,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T16:43:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191201/60330628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60330628&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0Q0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=c12b9c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60330628&h=0cd8fbe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191201/60330628</a><br />\n<br />\n(音樂)【12.7揭盅】《願榮光》狂吸12萬Like未入圍 網民推爆攞叱咤我最喜愛歌曲<br />\n <br />\n逆權運動未成功，抗爭歌《願榮光歸香港》成為港人心聲，商台明年1月1日舉行「叱咤樂壇頒獎禮」，很多網民均希望將代表香港人精神的《願榮光》推上頒獎舞台，成為本年度「我最喜愛的歌曲」。<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》由民間創作，沒有歌手演唱，而叱咤的投票機制，是以派台歌的播放率定勝負，6日前歌曲終於排除萬難派台，並登上商台「叱咤咤 派台歌」網頁，網民紛紛留言為歌曲打氣：「香港人的心聲！」、「願榮光歸香港， 加油！」、「香港人之歌」、「大家推爆佢」，至今歌曲已狂吸逾12萬like。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有網民誤會like夠10萬，就可以打入十大成為候選歌，在討論區開post：「你like咗《願榮光歸香港》未，夠10萬可以入十大投票，到時好似上年古天樂咁推爆佢，首歌可以攞獎。」商台對外事務部發言人回覆《蘋果》，澄清候選機制是上榜歌：「所有本年度上榜歌曲均自動入圍『叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的歌曲』候選名單，<a href=\"http://於12月9日開始廣邀樂迷透過my903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%96%BC12%E6%9C%889%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E5%BB%A3%E9%82%80%E6%A8%82%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8Emy903.com&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0Q0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=5a77db90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">於12月9日開始廣邀樂迷透過my903.com</a>、Hong Kong Toolbar網上、智能手機應用程式及商台節目重溫智能手機應用程式，以一人一票方式投選最後五強，再於當晚 (1月1日) 經過在場觀眾一人一票選出。」換言之，網民like爆10萬都冇用，要靠903的DJ們在節目中播歌，才有機會打上叱咤榜，自動成為候選歌，而昨日公佈的「903專業推介」20位，可惜《願榮光》仍未上榜。<br />\n<br />\n最後一期的叱咤榜將於下周六（7號）揭曉，究竟《願榮光》可不可以打入榜角逐「我最喜愛的歌曲」，還要靠903DJ努力播歌了。<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【匿名港警爆大鑊】<br />\n韓國KBS時事節目《時事直擊：香港 被自殺》<br />\n一按即睇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191201/large/1575201836_ba5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575201836_ba5e.jpg&h=34cd3cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191201/large/1575201836_aba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575201836_aba6.jpg&h=b20f05e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民希望《願榮光歸香港》可以成為今年「叱咤我最喜愛歌曲」，不過由於《願榮光》未曾上榜，暫沒有角逐該獎項。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191201/large/1575201851_6aa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575201851_6aa8.png&h=e51b2182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《願榮光》在商台網站，獲得12萬Like。一度有傳夠10萬Like就可以獲入圍資格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【We Connect】陳漢娜染血「單眼少女」造型影日本雜誌：永不放棄，永不原諒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【父子檔造勢】竹內涼真露點谷月曆 濕身晒結實胸肌"},{"pid":"e824e83d92cf0e2c29af880fe31049c201f47e7e","tid":1765228,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T00:17:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3d1504a4be53125652f0297794eb4f11bd7739bc","tid":1765228,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T00:21:03.000Z","msg":"DJ幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7fe027b98e7c6fe0dd9bb8e5ddf127a321de76","tid":1765228,"uid":25623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T00:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5d9f1b505adf13d5de824255e9b6d4b81718d5","tid":1765228,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191202/large/1575206674_9368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191202%2Flarge%2F1575206674_9368.jpg&h=2dea45ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《願榮光歸香港》包含香港人精神，充滿代表性。資料圖片"}]}